AN ACT
To repeal sections 41.216, 41.220, 41.430, 41.475, 42.300, 42.310, 42.312, 42.315, 105.265,
105.270, and 143.121, RSMo, and to enact in lieu thereof twenty-two new sections
relating to military affairs.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Missouri, as follows:
1 Section A. Sections 41.216, 41.220, 41.430, 41.475,
2 42.300, 42.310, 42.312, 42.315, 105.265, 105.270, and 143.121,
3 RSMo, are repealed and twenty-two new sections enacted in lieu
4 thereof, to be known as sections 41.216, 41.430, 41.475, 41.477,
5 41.598, 41.599, 41.1015, 41.1016, 41.1017, 41.1018, 41.1030,
6 42.028, 42.300, 42.310, 42.311, 42.312, 42.313, 42.315, 42.316,
7 105.265, 105.270, and 143.121, to read as follows:
